  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6776.69 sitting just above the 6775 GEX flip and between major gamma walls, dealers are in active hedging mode as we've just broken through a key level with surging gamma exposure (+23.8% in 1-min). The PIN regime with massive positive gamma concentration from 6775-6800 means dealers will aggressively sell any push toward 6785-6790 resistance and buy any dip toward 6775-6765 support. Watch 6785 (max positive gamma at 37.7B) as the critical resistance where dealer selling intensifies, and 6765 as the key support where dealer buying kicks in.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect tight range-bound trading between 6765-6785 with dealers capping moves in both directions.",
